  <brief_title>Exploratory Study of ART-123 for the Prevention of Cancer Treatment Related Symptoms in Patients With Postoperative Stage II / III Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Clinical Study of ART-123 for the Prevention of Cancer Treatment Related Symptoms in Patients With Postoperative Stage II / III Colon Cancer: a Multicenter Randomized Placebo-controlled Double-blind Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of ART-123</official_title>
