  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of ART-123 for the
      prevention of cancer treatment related symptoms in patients with postoperative stage II / III
      colon cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
